doctype html
html(lang='en')
  head
    meta(charset='UTF-8')
    meta(name='viewport' content='width=device-width,initial-scale=1')
    title About - MoodMeal
    link(rel='stylesheet' href='css/style.css')
    link(rel='preconnect' href='https://fonts.googleapis.com')
    link(rel='preconnect' href='https://fonts.gstatic.com' crossorigin)
    link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap' rel='stylesheet')
  body
    nav.navbar
      .nav-container
        .logo MoodMeal
        ul.nav-links
          li
            a(href='/') Home
          li
            a(href='/mood') Find Meal
          li
            a(href='/favorites') Favorites
          li
            a.active(href='/about') About
    section.about-section
      .container
        h1.page-title
          | About 
          span.gradient-text MoodMeal
        .about-content
          .about-intro
            .about-icon
            h2 Our Mission
            p.large-text.
              
              At MoodMeal, we believe that food is more than just sustenance - it's an emotional experience. Every mood deserves the perfect meal to complement it, whether you're celebrating, seeking comfort, or just looking for something exciting.
              
          .about-features
            .about-card
              .about-card-icon
              h3 The Concept
              p.
                
                MoodMeal was born from the simple observation that what we want to eat often depends on how we're feeling. We've taken the guesswork out of meal planning by matching dishes with emotional states.
                
            .about-card
              .about-card-icon
              h3 How It Works
              p.
                
                Select your current mood from our carefully curated list, and our system recommends meals that perfectly match your emotional state. It's that simple!
                
            .about-card
              .about-card-icon
              h3 Our Promise
              p.
                
                We're committed to making your meal decisions easier and more enjoyable. Every suggestion is thoughtfully chosen to enhance your dining experience based on your emotional needs.
                
          .about-stats
            .stat-card
              .stat-number 8+
              .stat-label Mood Categories
            .stat-card
              .stat-number 50+
              .stat-label Meal Options
            .stat-card
              .stat-number 100%
              .stat-label Satisfaction Goal
          .about-cta
            h2 Ready to find your perfect meal?
            p Start your journey with MoodMeal today and discover how the right meal can make all the difference.
            a.cta-button(href='/mood')
              span Get Started
              span.arrow 
    footer.footer
      p ┬⌐ 2025 MoodMeal. Made with for food lovers.
    script(src='js/script.js')
